- Technical Details
    - Tech Stack:
        - Vite 5 + Svelte 4
        - d3-geo, d3-contour, topojson-client
        - MapLibre GL JS 4
        - jsPDF + svg2pdf.js (vector PDF export)
        - UTIF (TIFF export)
        - JSZip (CNC layer export)
        - geotiff (NOAA ETOPO1 GeoTIFF decode)
    - Key Files:
        - src/pages/WorldMap.svelte — Tool 1
        - src/pages/TopoMap.svelte — Tool 2
        - src/lib/state.js — URL hash encode/decode
        - src/lib/export.js — SVG/PDF/PNG/TIFF export
        - src/lib/palettes.js — color palette presets
        - src/lib/elevation.js — Terrarium + ETOPO1 tile fetch
        - src/components/ — ExportPanel, ColorPicker, RegionSelector, ContourControls
        - public/data/ — world-110m.json, world-50m.json (Natural Earth TopoJSON)
        - .github/workflows/deploy.yml — GitHub Actions → gh-pages
    - Architecture Notes:
        - Static site, no backend
        - All state in URL hash (base64url JSON)
        - SVG-first rendering, raster export via canvas rasterization
        - Elevation: AWS Terrarium tiles (primary) + NOAA ETOPO1 ImageServer (supplemental)

